Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:08.14,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}在谜团重重的此世之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:10.15,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}将横行的棋子落下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:12.69,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}If I could burn it all down
